tically higher (by a factor of ~3) than\nthose obtained using n. This result may reflect the fact that for our sample\ngalaxies we do not find any correlation between L_bulge and n.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Dec 2006 17:29:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Dec 2006 23:30:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
