d M show that\nadLIGO can achieve SNR >~ 10 for some intermediate-mass binary black holes\n(IMBBHs) out to z ~ 1, and that LISA can see massive binary black holes (MBBHs)\nin the range 3x10^4 <~ M/M_Sun <~ 10^7 at SNR > 100 out to the earliest epochs\nof structure formation at z > 15.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Dec 2006 16:52:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 8 Sep 2007 23:25:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
